data.description: Welcome to this charming, turn-key 2 bedroom, 1 bath single-family home including a separate studio apartment. Perfectly suited for multi-generational living or as an income-generating opportunity. This property could EASILY be converted into a 3bd/2ba. Property is being offered fully furnished (including washer/dryer). Key upgrades include a New Roof 2022, new HVAC system with duct work, upgraded electrical panel, and new hot water heater. An outdoor enthusiast's dream, the property features a generously sized lot with an expansive backyard, providing ample space for parking boats, jet skis, or RVs. Additionally, a 10x12 shed equipped with water and electricity offers more options and practical storage solutions. Security motion sensor lights around the property and nest camera on front door. Centrally located in town, only 15 minutes to airports, beaches and downtown St Petersburg. Call for your private showing today!
